Test buffer sum works.
Let cells be array of 4 i32 containing 1, 2, 3, 4.
Let total be 0.
For each index i of cells: total becomes total plus cells at i.
Expect total is equal to 10.

Test owned buffer move works.
Let cells be owned buffer of 4 i32 containing 1, 2, 3, 4.
Let copy be owned buffer copied from cells.
Expect length of copy is equal to 4.
Expect copy at 0 is equal to 1.
